				<img id="home-img" class="spacer margin" src="img/photo1.jpg"><p>Welcome to the Hansen School District. We are a progressive rural school district serving approximately 350 students in grades PreK-12. The district boasts excellent instructional staff and up to date technology. Through aggressive grant writing, we have been able to supplement our curriculum and resources to allow teachers to be creative in meeting the needs of our students. The grants we were awarded last year include the Idaho School Improvement Grant, Monsanto, STEM, 21st Century Community Learning Centers, and the I3 Scale Up Writing.
                </p>

                <p>We value parents input and invite you to visit the school, call your childâ€™s teacher or principal, attend Board meetings and athletic activities and in general be a part of our community.
                </p>

                <p>So, if you are new welcome and if you are returning welcome back! This is truly a great district and we all feel fortunate to be a part of it.
                </p>
