                    <a href="http://cdc.gov/COVID19"><img style="float:right; width:50%;padding-left:20px; padding-right:20px" src="/img%5Cgraphics%5C2019-coronavirus.png"></a>
                    <p>This is an emerging, rapidly changing situation and Hansen School District will follow the guidance of South Central Public Health as it progresses. For questions please contact your physician or the local department of health. We encourage you to keep up to date about 2019-nCoV in our area, you will find links to information on the <a href="/coronavirus/whatis">What is Coronavirus</a> page.</p>

                    <p>District updates and information can be found on our Coronavirus information page at <a href="https://www.hansenschools.org/coronavirus">www.hanenschools.org/coronavirus</a>. Here you will find updates as to what we are doing in response to the coronavirus as well as links to resources for distance learning, meal programm, and internet services.
                    </p>

