                        <p>The district operates on a 4 day school week, with office hours Monday- Thursday 8:00-5:00. The school office hours are Monday- Thursday 7:45- 4:15. Please stop in and see us anytime. Visitors must sign in at the offices before gaining entrance to any classrooms, hallways, or other school grounds. Visitors will be given a badge to wear while on campus, and are expected to check out at the office before departing. All school buildings are to remain secure throughout the day. Safety is a top priority at Hansen School District, please help us maintain our security!</p>
